decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing control elements to disrupt the opponent's strategy while building towards a powerful end game. By combining the abilities of Miara and Tevesh, the deck aims to control the board through a combination of removal spells, hand disruption, and powerful planeswalkers. With a variety of removal options and versatile threats, the deck can adapt to different matchups and handle a wide range of threats. The inclusion of cards like Thoughtseize, Liliana of the Veil, and Ugin, the Ineffable helps the deck maintain card advantage and disrupt the opponent's resources. Ultimately, the deck aims to outvalue and outmaneuver the opponent through a combination of control and powerful threats.
